{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-spine-condition-listing-js","path":"/spine-condition/chronic-back-neck-pain/","result":{"data":{"wpSpineCondition":{"title":"Chronic Back & Neck Pain","slug":"chronic-back-neck-pain","content":"<p>Chronic back and neck pain can develop due to muscle strain, poor posture, disc degeneration, or long-term spinal stress. The pain may interfere with movement, posture, sleep, and daily activities over time. Some patients experience stiffness, headaches, or pain radiating into the arms or legs. Proper evaluation helps identify the underlying cause and guide treatment.</p>\n","featuredImage":null,"spineConditionsPost":{"desciption":"  <div className=\"section-title-wrp\">\r\n            <h2>Treatments & Procedures</h2>\r\n            <p className=\"treatments-intro\">\r\n              Persistent spinal pain affecting posture, mobility, and daily activities.\r\n            </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n"}},"allWpSpineCondition":{"nodes":[{"title":"Slipped or Herniated Disc","slug":"slipped-or-herniated-disc","databaseId":130,"menuOrder":1},{"title":"Sciatica & Nerve Compression","slug":"sciatica-nerve-compression","databaseId":157,"menuOrder":2},{"title":"Cervical Spine Disorders","slug":"cervical-spine-disorders","databaseId":158,"menuOrder":3},{"title":"Lumbar Spine Disorders","slug":"lumbar-spine-disorders","databaseId":159,"menuOrder":4},{"title":"Spinal Stenosis","slug":"spinal-stenosis","databaseId":160,"menuOrder":5},{"title":"Scoliosis & Spine Deformities","slug":"scoliosis-spine-deformities","databaseId":161,"menuOrder":6},{"title":"Spine Trauma & Fractures","slug":"spine-trauma-fractures","databaseId":162,"menuOrder":7},{"title":"Osteoporotic Compression Fractures","slug":"osteoporotic-compression-fractures","databaseId":163,"menuOrder":8},{"title":"Craniovertebral Junction Disorders","slug":"craniovertebral-junction-disorders","databaseId":164,"menuOrder":9},{"title":"Spinal Infections & Tuberculosis","slug":"spinal